@node BANDA "Bandage"

@{b}Bandage@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = W
Artist  = Rebecca Guay

Text(SH): Prevent 1 damage to any creature or player.
          Draw a card.

Flavor Text: @{i}Takara shook with guilt. She knew the last image her father
              had seen was her sword flashing toward him.@{ub}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node CALMI "Calming Licid"

@{b}Calming Licid@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Summon Licid (2/2)
Cost    = 2W
Artist  = D. Alexander Gregory

Text(SH): <WT>: Calming Licid loses this ability and becomes a creature
          enchantment that reads "Enchanted creature cannot attack" instead
          of a creature. Move Calming Licid onto target creature. You may
          pay W to end this effect.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node CHANG "Change of Heart"

@{b}Change of Heart@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = SH(C)
Type    = Instant
Cost    = W
Artist  = Ron Spencer

Text(SH): Buyback 3 (You may pay an additional 3 when you play this spell.
          If you do, put it into your hand instead of your graveyard as
          part of the spell's effect.)
          Target creature cannot attack this turn.


 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
