@{b}Contemplation@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = SH(U)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 1WW
Artist  = Brom

Text(SH): Whenever you successfully cast a spell, gain 1 life.

Flavor Text: @{i}"How fascinating it is to watch the machinations of
