 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node HIDDE "Hidden Retreat"

@{b}Hidden Retreat@{ub}

Color   = White
Rarity  = SH(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 2W
Artist  = Terese Nielsen

Text(SH): Choose a card in your hand and put it on top of your library:
          Prevent all damage from an instant or sorcery. (Treat further
          damage from that source normally.)

Flavor Text: @{i}After an hour in the hidey-hole, Squee seriously pondered
              the advantages of danger over boredom.@{ub}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
